{l s='The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) gives people the right to limit the use of their data in certain situations.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='In the GDPR (Article 18) this right is described as the right to restrict processing.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='The right to restrict processing applies in situations that meet one of the following criteria:' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='- Data may be incorrect' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='- The processing is unlawful' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='- Data is no longer needed' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='- The subject concerned objects to processing' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='If someone objects to the processing of his or her personal data you must stop processing this data.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='Unless you submit compelling legitimate reasons for the processing that outweighs the interests, rights and freedoms of the person concerned.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='As long as it is not clear whether your grounds are more important, you may not process the data.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='If you provided the relevant personal data to other parties then you must inform these organizations that you have limited the use of the subjects data.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='And inform them they have to do the same.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='You also have to inform the subject which organizations you have informed.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='Inform people about their right to restrict processing in the text block above.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='Make sure you inform them how they can contact you.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
{l s='The easiest way is linking to the contact form of your shop.' mod='tbgdpr'}<br>
